rows.label: tlk42100181_04_msg0001
rows.name:
The Divine Beast went vroom and
moved, mo! It was a surprise, mo!!

rows.label: tlk42100181_04_msg0002
rows.name:
But Magomago isn't scared,
mo! Because Grampypon is
here, it's no big deal, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100181_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Grampypon said that it's the
Nopon spirit to bring in goods
at times like this, mo!
